	* mempool.c: Include string.h to kill warning.

	* testjit.c: Add typecast to kill warning.

	* x86.brg: Include string.h to eliminate warning.

	* emit-x86.c (tree_allocate_regs): Fix arguments to g_warning to
	kill warning.

